Program: Outlook
Title: Outlook Weekend: The Laws of Love
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w3cswt5p
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 29 Apr 2018
When Jim met John, it was instant love. Despite John battling terminal illness and the fact that same sex marriage wasn't legal in their state, the couple was determined to get married. What they didn't realise is that their union would change the course of US legal history. Image: Jim and John on their wedding day on an aeroplane Credit: Jim Obergefell Show less